Here and Now: 3 (BURN THIS CASSETTE)
This has to be burnt if you want the following:

Burning this gives you access to a lil secret listening party inside the tower featuring the music of @astonarcher and who knows maybe you'll be able to pick up a couple of tracks. 

This is for future ticketholders who will attend the Here and Now Edition 3 experience.

Important: Burn this from the address you intend to purchase a ticket from.
